CHAT
====

Usage: chat <message>     - Send a message to global chat
       chat on            - Subscribe to chat
       chat off           - Unsubscribe from chat
       chat history [N]   - View last N messages (default 20)

Global in-character chat channel. Messages are seen by all online players
who have chat enabled. Chat history is saved, so you can catch up on
messages you missed while offline.

Examples:
  chat Hello everyone!
  chat off
  chat history 50

Alternative: Use 'history chat [N]' to view chat history.

See also: ooc, channels, history
